data.description: Introducing a charming two-story townhome nestled in the serene and secure community of ''Emerald Preserve'' in Jacksonville, Florida. This delightful residence offers a perfect blend of comfort and style, and provides a peaceful retreat for relaxing after a long day at work. This tastefully designed townhome boasts two spacious bedrooms,two full baths and one half bath. The heart of this home is its modern kitchen, equipped with new stainless steel appliances including a built-in microwave. The inclusion of a one-car garage provides secure parking and some additional storage space. Enjoy the beauty of nature from your covered and screened patio with a picturesque view of a small pond, complemented by the lush greenery of the wooded preserve. This home offers a harmonious blend of natural beauty, and community comfort. Experience the joy of coming home to a place that not only meets your practical needs but also provides a serene and aesthetically pleasing environment. See it today!
